<P>It is indeed a <HI>whole Body</HI> of his <HI>practical Divi|nity,</HI>
however <HI>summ'd</HI> up in so small a <HI>System.</HI>
For the <HI>whole Duty</HI> of a <HI>Christian</HI> do's consist in
<HI>two things;</HI> first (by way of <HI>privation) in casting
