which were yesterday forbid by his <HI>Majesties</HI>
excellent <HI>Proclamation;</HI> (for these are some of
the <HI>works of darkness,</HI> the very <HI>worst use</HI> that men
can make of a <HI>Deliverance,)</HI> next he tells us in
