<PB N="8" REF="11">
and taking a copy from his <HI>example;</HI> by having
a <HI>fellowship with his death,</HI> and a <HI>conformity</HI> to his
<HI>sufferings;</HI> For <HI>this</HI> is here meant by the <HI>Armour
of Light.</HI></P>
<P>And each of these is improved by <HI>three</HI> main
