Times, that I may say in the very <HI>language</HI>
(though not in the very <HI>sense)</HI> of our Bles<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ed
Saviour,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Luke 4. 21.</NOTE> <HI>This day is this Scripture fulfilled in our
Ears.</HI> For,</P>
<P>We have had both our <HI>Iews,</HI> and our <HI>Gno|sticks</HI>
