<P>VVhen we were <HI>dull,</HI> and in the <HI>dark,</HI> and
knew not the Happiness we injoy'd, <HI>whilst</HI> we
injoy'd it; when we could not comport with so
<HI>hard a lesson,</HI> as the<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">1 Pet. 2. 13, 14.</NOTE> <HI>submitting our selves for the
