<P>A
SERMON
PREACHED
At St. <HI>MARGARETS WESTMINSTER</HI>
by the Order of the Honourable the House
OF
COMMONS
IN
PARLIAMENT Assembled,
Upon the 29^t^h Day of <HI>MAY,</HI> being the Anniver|sary
Day of the
KING'S and KINGDOM'S
RESTAURATION.
MD.DC.LXI.</P>
<P>Legum Conditores Festos dies instituerunt, ut ad hilaritatem ho|mines
