<PB N="99" REF="56">
commonly</HI> Crest-fallen,<NOTE PLACE="marg"><GAP DESC="foreign">. Thucyd. lib. 2. p. 161.</NOTE> <HI>and do</HI> remit <HI>of their cou|rage
against a</HI> second <HI>Encounter, as soon as they
