<P>Secondly the <HI>People</HI> to whom <HI>directed;</HI> And
These are <HI>imply'd</HI> in the Pronown <HI>Ye.</HI> My <HI>Israel,</HI>
my Chosen, the peculiar Lot of mine Inheri|tance,
<HI>Audite Vos, hear Ye.</HI></P>
<P>Thirdly the <HI>Audience,</HI> or <HI>Attention,</HI> which is
