it must necessarily follow, that to a <HI>sin|ner</HI>
who is <HI>Incorrigible, Death</HI> it self becomes a
<HI>Curtesy.</HI> The reason is, because it renders him
<HI>less unhappy,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Mali c&ugrave;m Supplicio <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">a|rent, inest iis aliquid alte|rius mali, ipsa Impunitas.</NOTE> than he would otherwise have
been. For that even in <HI>Hell</HI> there is <HI>Room</HI> for
