Rom. 13. 2. Hanc esse mentem<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">Vide Tom. 2. H<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">mil. 4.</NOTE> <HI>Ecclesiae nostrae,</HI>
