<PB N="278" REF="144">
<HI>Iournies,</HI> whilst yet he could not either<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg"><GAP DESC="foreign"> Ponitur pro <GAP DESC="foreign">. nam <HI>addu|cendi</HI> verbum ponimus in eo qui pedibus eat: id quod de Christo in e&acirc; aetate dici non p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">terat. <HI>Castalio in locum.</HI></NOTE> <HI>go,</HI> or
