<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">Chap. 13. Vers. 15.</NOTE> were immediately claimed by their
<HI>preserver.</HI> who besides the <HI>common Interest</HI> which
he had in them as his <HI>Creatures,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Exod. 1. 22.</NOTE> did farher <HI>devote</HI>
