<PB N="279" REF="144">
He took the <HI>Levites</HI> unto Himself, (in
<HI>stead of all the first born of the Children of Israel,)</HI>
Yet were not the <HI>Levites</HI> so <HI>full</HI> a <HI>Ransome,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Num. 18. 16.</NOTE>
