with his<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">Vereor ne mendacii vel Adulationis contraham no|tam, si solu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> Populo Con|tradixero. <HI>p. 330. Edit. Lugd. p. 427. edit. Colon.</HI></NOTE> <HI>own opinion;</HI> as also with the opinion
of Cardinal<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">Veruntamen quia Populo testimonium perhibet [Cardinalis] ei usquequa&abque; Contradi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ere non praesumo, &amp;c. <HI>ibid.</HI></NOTE> <HI>Guido,</HI> whom the plain-hearted
