<HI>second)</HI> most <HI>Helpfull Engine.</HI></P>
<P>&sect;. 7. This does bring into my mind, what
I was told many Years since by an honourable
Friend,<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">Mr. Patrick Carew.</NOTE> (then when newly come out of <HI>Italy,</HI>
