of<NOTE N="b" PLACE="marg">Concil. Con|staniense prae|cipu&egrave; congre|gatum extin|guendi schis|matis Caus&acirc;, quis esset ve|rus Pontifex, vix agnosce|bat. <HI>V. Hist. Concil. &agrave; Paulo V. Edit. Tom. 4. p.</HI> 127.</NOTE> <HI>Constance</HI> and<NOTE N="c" PLACE="marg">Statim illud in Controver|siam venit, Nam Synodus Pisana in Illos potuerit ani|mad<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ertere, c&ugrave;m eorum al<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">uter ve|rus esset Pon|tif<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">. sed inter+is esse<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> non co<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="3 letters">aret. <HI>ib. p. seqq.</HI></NOTE> <HI>Pisa</HI> (whereof the <HI>former,</HI> by
