of <HI>Some.</HI> But then, with the help of that
<GAP DESC="foreign">, the <HI>meanest man</HI> is as <HI>omniscient,</HI> as is
his <HI>Roman Catholick Church;</HI> because (within
his <HI>determinate sphere)</HI> he must needs have a
<HI>knowledge</HI> of <HI>All</HI> he <HI>know's;</HI> and of <HI>more</HI> than she
<HI>know's</HI> the <HI>Roman Church</HI> hath <HI>no knowledge.</HI> So
again when he would shew how a <HI>creature</HI> may
