say was in an Error, for declaring it unlawful,
to <HI>paint</HI> in the windows or walls of <HI>Churches,</HI>
what is the <HI>object</HI> of <HI>Adoration.</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg"><HI>Concil. Nic. 2. Act.</HI> 4. Concil. Con|stant. quartu~ decrevit e<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">n|dem Imaginu~ cultum. <HI>Edit. Bin. Tom. 7. p.</HI> 1046.</NOTE> And so much
the rather will he believe it to be an <HI>Error,</HI> be|cause
