he not think it was an <HI>Error</HI> in the<NOTE N="*" PLACE="marg">Concil. Constanti|nop. III. Act. 13. Tom.. 5 lib. 211. Vide Notas in vitam Honor. Edit. Bin. Tom. 4. pag. 572. <GAP DESC="foreign">, &amp;c. Concil. Flor. definit. Edit. Bin. To. 8. p. 854.</NOTE> <HI>sixth General
Council,</HI> to <HI>condemn</HI> Pope <HI>Honorius</HI> as a <HI>Monothe|lite,</HI>
