<NOTE N="b" PLACE="marg"><GAP DESC="foreign">, &amp;c. <GAP DESC="foreign"> &amp;c. ibid. p. 325, 326.</NOTE> <HI>against the Canon</HI> of the <HI>Church of Rome,</HI> where|unto
is <HI>confronted</HI> the <HI>antient Canon,</HI> which is
