thither in<NOTE N="d" PLACE="marg">Hunc <HI>di|verso tramite</HI> Mortales Omnes co|nantur adi|pisci. <HI>Boeth. de Consol. Phi|los. l. 3. p.</HI> 98.</NOTE> <HI>several Rodes;</HI> 'tis plain that he who
lives <HI>longest,</HI> goes but the <HI>farthest</HI> way <HI>about,</HI> and
